                            <comment id="16097391" author="varuna" created="Sat, 22 Jul 2017 17:47:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes, constructor does not set the &lt;tt&gt;ignores&lt;/tt&gt;. I&apos;m providing patch for this. &lt;br/&gt;
Also need to check for other versions.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16097392" author="varuna" created="Sat, 22 Jul 2017 17:49:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;fixed constructor of &lt;tt&gt;LoaderOptions&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16097497" author="varuna" created="Sun, 23 Jul 2017 04:14:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;cassandra &lt;tt&gt;tag &amp;gt;= 3.4&lt;/tt&gt; are having this bug.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
