&lt;p&gt;committed to 3.11 and trunk as sha &lt;tt&gt;c3a19f3554113682b4d37fe6a7f49bc810e5ddf6&lt;/tt&gt;. Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16097646" author="varuna" created="Sun, 23 Jul 2017 14:34:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thank you so much!! It was my first patch which got accepted!! &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
